---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Submit a Product for Review — Filce.uk" description="Have a product you'd like reviewed on filce.uk? Here's how to submit and what to expect from our review process." canonicalPath="/work-with-me/">
  <div class="page-container">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="page-header">
        <h1>Submit a Product for Review</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Got a product that belongs on filce.uk?</p>
      </header>

      <div class="page-content prose">
        <p class="lead">We'd love to hear from you.</p>

        <h2>What We Review</h2>

        <p>We specialise in practical, hands-on reviews for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Home Automation</strong> — Smart devices, sensors, Home Assistant integrations</li>
          <li><strong>Networking</strong> — Routers, access points, switches, cameras</li>
          <li><strong>Tools & DIY</strong> — Workshop equipment, hobbyist tools</li>
          <li><strong>Tech Accessories</strong> — Phone cases, chargers, cables, gadgets</li>
          <li><strong>Pet Tech</strong> — GPS trackers, cameras, feeders, smart collars</li>
          <li><strong>Kitchen & Home</strong> — Practical gadgets for home life</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Our Review Style</h2>

        <p>We don't do surface-level unboxings. Our reviews include:</p>

        <ul>
          <li>✅ Real product photos (not press images)</li>
          <li>✅ Hands-on testing over days/weeks</li>
          <li>✅ Practical use cases from a real home</li>
          <li>✅ Honest pros and cons</li>
          <li>✅ SEO-optimised for discoverability</li>
          <li>✅ Affiliate purchase links</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Before You Contact Us</h2>

        <p><strong>We need:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>A UK-relevant product (shipping to UK)</li>
          <li>A product that fits our categories</li>
          <li>Genuine confidence in your product quality</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>We don't accept:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Paid positive reviews</li>
          <li>Products we can't test properly</li>
          <li>Products outside our expertise</li>
          <li>Vape, CBD, gambling, or adult products</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How to Submit</h2>

        <p><strong>Email us at:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@filce.uk">contact@filce.uk</a></p>

        <p><strong>Include:</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>Product name and category</li>
          <li>Brief description</li>
          <li>UK retail price</li>
          <li>Your website/product page URL</li>
          <li>Whether you can provide a review unit</li>
          <li>Any timeline requirements</li>
        </ol>

        <h2>What Happens Next</h2>

        <ol>
          <li><strong>Review</strong> — We'll assess fit within 48 hours</li>
          <li><strong>Confirm</strong> — If accepted, we'll arrange delivery</li>
          <li><strong>Test</strong> — 2-4 weeks of hands-on use</li>
          <li><strong>Draft</strong> — We'll share for factual accuracy (not editorial control)</li>
          <li><strong>Publish</strong> — Live on filce.uk</li>
          <li><strong>Share</strong> — Social promotion (optional, by agreement)</li>
        </ol>

        <h2>Review Unit Policy</h2>

        <ul>
          <li><strong>Keep or Return:</strong> We'll discuss what works for you</li>
          <li><strong>Disclosure:</strong> We'll clearly state if a product was provided</li>
          <li><strong>Honesty:</strong> We won't guarantee a positive review</li>
          <li><strong>Timeline:</strong> We'll agree on a realistic deadline upfront</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Questions?</h2>

        <p>Email <a href="mailto:contact@filce.uk">contact@filce.uk</a> — we respond within 48-72 hours.</p>

        <hr>

        <p><em>We're actively building our review portfolio. If you're a brand looking for authentic coverage, get in touch.</em></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
